  "body": "Enable remote Validators to subscribe to events from the Beacon Node.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Multiple validator nodes should be able to connect to a single Beacon Node\r\n* No polling behaviour from Validators, events should be pushed to them\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nThis will be implemented using a WebSocket endpoint. For the time being, this will be separate from the Beacon Node API, and will be running as a separate service. But in the future, they might be joined together.\r\n",
